17 license. Provided, that the ABLE Commission shall have the
18 authority to designate areas to be excluded from the licensed
19 premises solely for the purpose of:
20 a. allowing the presence and consumption of alcoholic
21 beverages by private parties which are closed to the
22 general public, or
23 b. allowing the services of a caterer serving alcoholic
24 beverages provided by a private party.
